{"tid":655300,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完marvel睇翻dc套正義聯盟","createTime":"2018-05-06T11:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T17:18:22.000Z","uid":87428,"like":61,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9a04621b7f593b9b074d25899fd0fc154c9deece","tid":655300,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"發覺dc拍套野 應該冇budget <br />\n錢應該去哂片酬<br />\nCg  vfx 唔夠錢整<br />\n好多時都係zoom 近角色大頭 <br />\n借d意 整少d effects係環境到<br />\n望落好似80 90年代 遠景好假<br />\n一開始蝙蝠俠打賊<br />\n至Superman復活見老母<br />\n到最後打boss render都唔夠<br />\n<br />\n連受城市襲擊既市民都冇錢請<br />\n得對俄羅斯家庭走佬<br />\n<br />\n人都沒錢請 最後超人救棟樓當交數<br />\n<br />\n仲有某d位實在太兒戲<br />\n唔講之前個套batman vs superman 媽媽同名<br />\n蝙蝠俠搵水行俠 可以轉個頭 就一齊行<br />\n見到superman 復活 佢條女叫一叫<br />\n超人見到女就攬女 唔再發脾氣 打隊友 飛走<br />\n<br />\nGag位都無無謂謂<br />\n水行俠無啦啦講廢話 成件事好odd<br />\n想學marvel咁 但又唔太好笑<br />\n<br />\n主體劇情接受得到 重係打大boss happy ending<br />\n<br />\n利申:睇完無限之石 翻去睇正義"},{"pid":"4393357edde660ab5f425124dfbf1b74178b42e6","tid":655300,"uid":89199,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56b3fd74239ba30be6dacb699cb74de2b7d6485b","tid":655300,"uid":66957,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"樓主呢到我頂住 你走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8683ac52124262d31a25ae8a2cc67bbb24b0e9","tid":655300,"uid":90634,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4393357edde660ab5f425124dfbf1b74178b42e6","tid":655300,"uid":89199,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"dc cls 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f434c942b57d3a2041f1c0798b815e737da1157","tid":655300,"uid":3912,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T12:11:04.000Z","msg":"呢個世界一直都係風水輪流轉咁<br />\n呢個威完之後到另一個威，果個威完又到返呢一個<br />\n十年